CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1962, pg. 16 reads: "Getting Out The Vote - Shown getting-out the vote are (left to right): Claude Allen; Wannetta Junt; Robert Pryor; Ella Harris; Roland Matthews; Charles McCormack; Grace English; Matthew English; Clarence M. Payne Jr., and Pat Adams, team captain. They are shown at Homewood and Frankstown Aves., as the NAACP team members spread throughout town to get out the vote. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: NAACP members including Claude Allen, Wannetta Junt, Robert Pryor, Ella Harris, Roland Matthews, Charles McCormack, Grace English, Matthew English, Clarence M. Payne Jr., and Pat Adams, campaigning for voter registration outside of drug store on corner of Homewood and Frankstown Avenues
